General.Name: Terragen Holdings Ltd
General.Description: Terragen Holdings Limited engages in the research, development, production, and sale of biological products for agriculture sector in Australia and New Zealand. It offers Mylo, an animal feed supplement; and Great Land, a liquid biological soil conditioner that improves soil characteristics. The company was incorporated in 1996 and is based in Coolum Beach, Australia.
